SectionHowItWorks.createListingLink: Everytime you book through Goodwings Experience our partners receive money to make the world a better place
SectionHowItWorks.part1Text: Goodwings’ nonprofit partners all around the world have added inspiring activities for you to easily book. You can search by location or type of experience. You can also filter by social impact focus, for example experiences focused on People or Planet.
SectionHowItWorks.part2Text: When you’ve found what you want, you simply ask about availability and get more details about the experience by reaching out to the Goodwings partner hosting the experience. All directly through this site.
SectionHowItWorks.part3Text: When you’re ready, it’s fast, easy and secure to book and pay for the experience. Besides a transaction fee, the entire amount paid will go directly to the nonprofit organisation hosting the experience. Following the payment, you will receive all the necessary practical details about the experience.
